template_sql:
select TOP c1 p.objid,
           p.run,
           p.rerun,
           p.camcol,
           p.field,
           p.obj,
           p.type,
           p.ra,
           p.dec,
           p.u,
           p.g,
           p.r,
           p.i,
           p.z,
           p.Err_u,
           p.Err_g,
           p.Err_r,
           p.Err_i,
           p.Err_z
from fGetNearbyObjEq(c2, c3, c4) n,
     PhotoPrimary p
where n.objID=p.objID

select ra,dec,psfMag_u,
              psfMag_g,
              psfMag_r,
              psfMag_i,
              psfMag_z,
              petroRc1_r,
              probPSF,
              psfMagErr_u,
              psfMagErr_g,
              psfMagErr_r,
              psfMagErr_i,
              psfMagErr_z,
              p.objid
from (PhotoTag p
      inner join fGetObjFromRectEq(c2, c3, c4, c5) r on p.objid=r.objid)

select r.run,
       r.rerun,
       r.camcol,
       r.field,
       f.fieldId,
       r.stripe,
       r.strip,
       r.ra,
       r.dec,
       r.raMin,
       r.raMax,
       r.decMin,
       r.decMax,
       r.mu,
       r.nu,
       r.incl,
       r.node,
       r.a,
       r.b,
       r.c,
       r.d,
       r.e,
       r.f,
       f.quality,
       f.a_u,
       f.b_u,
       f.c_u,
       f.d_u,
       f.e_u,
       f.f_u,
       f.a_g,
       f.b_g,
       f.c_g,
       f.d_g,
       f.e_g,
       f.f_g,
       f.a_r,
       f.b_r,
       f.c_r,
       f.d_r,
       f.e_r,
       f.f_r,
       f.a_i,
       f.b_i,
       f.c_i,
       f.d_i,
       f.e_i,
       f.f_i,
       f.a_z,
       f.b_z,
       f.c_z,
       f.d_z,
       f.e_z,
       f.f_z,
       dbo.fGetUrlFitsCFrame(f.fieldId, c1) as u_url,
       dbo.fGetUrlFitsCFrame(f.fieldId, c2) as g_url,
       dbo.fGetUrlFitsCFrame(f.fieldId, c3) as r_url,
       dbo.fGetUrlFitsCFrame(f.fieldId, c4) as i_url,
       dbo.fGetUrlFitsCFrame(f.fieldId, c5) as z_url
from dbo.fGetNearbyFrameEq(c6, c7, c8, c9) n,
     Frame r,
     Field f
where f.fieldId=r.fieldId
  and r.fieldId=n.fieldId
  and r.zoom=c10

select top c1 c2 + cast(p.objId as varchar(c3)) + c4 + cast(p.objId as varchar(c5)) + c6 as objID,
           p.run,
           p.rerun,
           p.camcol,
           p.field,
           p.obj,
           p.type,
           p.ra,
           p.dec,
           p.u,
           p.g,
           p.r,
           p.i,
           p.z,
           p.Err_u,
           p.Err_g,
           p.Err_r,
           p.Err_i,
           p.Err_z
from fGetNearbyObjEq(c7, c8, c9) n,
     PhotoPrimary p
where n.objID=p.objID

select name,
       type
from DBObjects
where type=c1
  and access=c2
  and name not in (c3,
                   c4)
order by name

select c1 + cast(p.objId as varchar(c2)) + c3 + cast(p.objId as varchar(c4)) + c5 as objID,
       p.run,
       p.rerun,
       p.camcol,
       p.field,
       p.obj,
       p.type,
       p.ra,
       p.dec,
       p.u,
       p.g,
       p.r,
       p.i,
       p.z,
       p.Err_u,
       p.Err_g,
       p.Err_r,
       p.Err_i,
       p.Err_z
from fGetNearbyObjEq(c6, c7, c8) n,
     PhotoPrimary p
where n.objID=p.objID

select top c1 p.objID,
           p.run,
           p.rerun,
           p.camcol,
           p.field,
           p.obj,
           p.type,
           p.ra,
           p.dec,
           p.u,
           p.g,
           p.r,
           p.i,
           p.z,
           p.Err_u,
           p.Err_g,
           p.Err_r,
           p.Err_i,
           p.Err_z
from fGetNearbyObjEq(c2, c3, c4) n,
     PhotoPrimary p
where n.objID=p.objID

select top c1 c2 + cast(p.objId as varchar(c3)) + c4 + cast(p.objId as varchar(c5)) + c6 as objID,
           p.run,
           p.rerun,
           p.camcol,
           p.field,
           p.obj,
           p.type,
           p.ra,
           p.dec,
           p.u,
           p.g,
           p.r,
           p.i,
           p.z,
           p.Err_u,
           p.Err_g,
           p.Err_r,
           p.Err_i,
           p.Err_z
from fGetNearbyObjEq(c7, c8, c9) n
join PhotoPrimary p on n.objID=p.objID

select c1 + cast(p.apstar_id as varchar(c2)) + c3 + cast(p.apstar_id as varchar(c4)) + c5 as apstar_id,
       p.apogee_id,
       p.ra,
       p.dec,
       p.glon,
       p.glat,
       p.vhelio_avg,
       p.vscatter,
       a.teff,
       a.logg,
       a.metals
from apogeeStar p
join fGetNearbyApogeeStarEq(c6, c7, c8) n on p.apstar_id=n.apstar_id
join aspcapStar a on a.apstar_id = p.apstar_id

select name,
       type
from DBObjects
where type=c1
  and name not in (c2,
                   c3)
order by name

select description
from DBObjects
where name=c1

select top c1 p.objid,
           p.ra,
           p.dec,
           dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,
           u,
           g,
           r,
           i,
           z,
           Err_u,
           Err_g,
           Err_r,
           Err_i,
           Err_z,
           psfMag_u,
           psfMagErr_u,
           psfMag_g,
           psfMagErr_g,
           psfMag_r,
           psfMagErr_r,
           psfMag_i,
           psfMagErr_i,
           psfMag_z,
           psfMagErr_z
from PhotoPrimary p,
     dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(c2, c3, c4) n
where p.objId=n.objId

select name,
       ucd
from dbcolumns
where tablename = c1
  and (name like c2
       or name like c3
       or name like c4
       or name like c5
       or name like c6
       or name like c7
       or name like c8
       or name like c9
       or name like c10
       or name like c11
       or name like c12
       or name like c13
       or name like c14
       or name like c15
       or name like c16
       or name like c17
       or name like c18
       or name like c19
       or name like c20
       or name like c21
       or name like c22
       or name like c23
       or name like c24
       or name like c25)

select name,
       type
from DBObjects
where name like c1
  or name like c2
order by name

select [indexMapID],
       [code],
       [type],
       [tableName],
       [fieldList],
       [foreignKey]
from IndexMap
where tableName=c1
order by [indexMapId]

select s.z,
       p.petroRad_z
from photoObj p
join specObj s on s.bestObjID = p.objID
where s.bestObjID = c1

select z,
       ra, dec, bestObjID
from specObj
where class = c1
  and ra between c2 and c3
  and dec between c4 and c5
  and z between c6 and c7

select distinct p.ra,
                p.dec,
                p.objid,
                p.run,
                p.rerun,
                p.camcol,
                p.field,
                s.z,
                s.plate,
                s.mjd,
                s.fiberID,
                s.specobjid,
                s.runc1d,
                s.instrument
from PhotoObjAll as p
join SpecObjAll s on p.objID = s.bestObjID
where ((p.ra between c2 and c3)
       and (p.dec between c4 and c5))
select dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdAllEq(c1, c2, c3) as specObjID

select distinct p.ra,
                p.dec,
                p.clean,
                p.u,
                p.g,
                p.r,
                p.i,
                p.z
from PhotoObjAll as p
where ((p.ra between c1 and c2)
       and (p.dec between c3 and c4))

select P.objid,
       P.ra,
       P.dec,
       P.petroMag_r,
       P.petroMagErr_r,
       P.deVRad_r,
       P.petroRad_r,
       P.deVPhi_r,
       P.deVAB_r,
       P.rowc_r,
       P.colc_r,
       P.run,
       P.rerun,
       P.camcol,
       P.field
from PhotoObjAll P
where P.objid = c1

select ra,dec,dered_u,
              dered_g,
              dered_r,
              dered_i,
              dered_z,
              Err_u,
              Err_g,
              Err_r,
              Err_i,
              Err_z,
              flags_r,
              run
from Galaxy
where ra between c1 and c2
  and dec between c3 and c4

select p.objid,
       p.ra,
       p.dec,
       p.r,
       s.specobjid,
       s.z,
       dbo.fSpecZWarningN(s.zWarning) as warning,
       s.plate,
       s.mjd,
       s.fiberid
from PhotoObj as p
join SpecObj as s on s.bestobjid = p.objid
where p.ra < c1
  and p.ra > c2
  and p.dec < c3
  and p.dec > c4
